snippet.title: Passing Memories - Emotional Composition (Improvised Piano)
snippet.description:
I've been really enjoying improvising and coming up with ideas for compositions! In this one, I've tried vary with different styles and moods, let me know which parts you like! any thoughts and ideas are appreciated. I've named this improvised composition 'Passing Memories' as while I was playing particular near the end, I was thinking about old stories and memories and it heavily inspired my improvisation.
